@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Service Status State Transition

[*] --> Active : Service created

Active --> Inactive : Admin deactivates
Active --> Archived : Service discontinued

Inactive --> Active : Admin reactivates
Inactive --> Archived : Permanently removed

Archived --> [*] : Service deleted\n(if no history)

Active : Available for booking
Active : Displayed to customers
Active : Can be ordered

Inactive : Hidden from customers
Inactive : Cannot be booked
Inactive : Can be reactivated

Archived : No longer offered
Archived : Historical records only
Archived : Cannot be reactivated

@enduml
